# text: But my dream here is that , if you can make it economic , and meet the CO2 constraints , then the skeptics say , okay , I do n't care that it does n't put out CO2 , I kind of wish it did put out CO2 , but I guess I 'll accept it because it 's cheaper than what 's come before .
